  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Associate Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>World No.1 player in industry is hiring Associate Engineers</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Company Introduction</strong></p>\n<p>Angel Group owns the world’s largest share for the manufacture of casino playing cards and related equipment. Angel has 70 years of history; started from Japan and now has offices in USA, Singapore, Australia, Macau, Philippines, Mexico and France with a total of over 500 employees in the world. We are the first company in the Jurong Innovative District and this four-storey building is our next regional Headquarters, with an R&amp;D Centre and factory.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Execute production as per production schedule and meet targeted output as set by management.</li>\n  <li>Perform initial level of troubleshooting of equipment-related problems to minimise downtime.</li>\n  <li>Interact with staff support to ensure smooth and optimum level of machine operational efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Establish effective preventive maintenance.</li>\n  <li>To control the quality of outputs using advanced technologies.</li>\n  <li>To control the flow of various goods and materials through digital quantity monitoring system.</li>\n  <li>Mange multiple priorities.</li>\n  <li>Other related tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required (Fresh Graduates welcome)</li>\n  <li>Any relevant Diploma in Engineering</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Location : West</li>\n  <li>Company coach available from Jurong East MRT</li>\n  <li>Working Hrs : 8:30AM – 5:30PM Off on Sat &amp; Sun</li>\n  <li>Lunch and uniform including safety gear are provided.</li>\n</ul>",
